author: ssrothman
body: This PR is a companion to cmssw PR [#42950](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/42950), which address issue [#41060](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/issues/41060). This PR contains the updated model config for the change from execution with the Triton ensemble backend to execution of a single combined pure pytorch model.
title: Updates to weights for deterministic evaluation of photonDRN
